steps.instruction:
- Preheat oven to 400F
- Cook Macaroni according to box instructions
- Drain pasta
- Return pasta to pot
- Add butter, sliced into individual tablespoons
- Stir to melt butter
- In a large bowl beat eggs and mix with cottage cheese, sour creme, both the cheeses, milk and seasonings
- Fold in the buttered macaroni
- Pour into 9x13 inch baking dish and cover with aluminum foil
- Bake at 400F for 30 minutes
- Remove foil and bake for 10 more minutes
